description.en: Application profile of Czech Core Metadata Model.
Semantic model for the profile

label.en: View for Czech Core Metadata Model

description.en: View model for the profile

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Person. Physical person.
description.en: Data structure for Person. Physical person.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Agent. Any entity carrying out actions with respect to the entities Catalogue and the Catalogued Resources.
description.en: Data structure for Agent. Any entity carrying out actions with respect to the entities Catalogue and the Catalogued Resources.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Distribuce. Konkrétní reprezentace datové sady. Datová sada může být dostupná v různých serializacích, které se mohou navzájem lišit různými způsoby, mimo jiné přirozeným jazykem, media-typem či formátem, schematickou organizací, časovým a prostorovým rozlišením, úrovní detailu či profily (které mohou specifikovat některé či všechny tyto rozdíly).
description.en: Data structure for Distribution. A specific representation of a dataset. A dataset might be available in multiple serializations that may differ in various ways, including natural language, media-type or format, schematic organization, temporal and spatial resolution, level of detail or profiles (which might specify any or all of the above).

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Contact details. Contact details such as telephone, e-mail address etc.
description.en: Data structure for Contact details. Contact details such as telephone, e-mail address etc.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Resource. Resource represents any resource, physical or digital, that is related to the described dataset.
description.en: Data structure for Resource. Resource represents any resource, physical or digital, that is related to the described dataset.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Location. Spatial region, named place or geometry representation of a place related to the dataset.
description.en: Data structure for Location. Spatial region, named place or geometry representation of a place related to the dataset.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Time reference. A date on which something relative to the resource has happened.
description.en: Data structure for Time reference. A date on which something relative to the resource has happened.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Funding reference. Information about financial support (funding) for the resource being registered.
description.en: Data structure for Funding reference. Information about financial support (funding) for the resource being registered.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Funder identifier. Uniquely identifies a funding entity, according to various types.
description.en: Data structure for Funder identifier. Uniquely identifies a funding entity, according to various types.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Terms of use. Terms of use defines overall conditions and rights regarding access and usage  of dataset.
description.en: Data structure for Terms of use. Terms of use defines overall conditions and rights regarding access and usage  of dataset.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Resource to Agent Relationship. An association class for attaching additional information to a relationship between Dataset and Agent.
description.en: Data structure for Resource to Agent Relationship. An association class for attaching additional information to a relationship between Dataset and Agent.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Resource agent role type. An idea or notion; a unit of thought.
description.en: Data structure for Resource agent role type. An idea or notion; a unit of thought.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Application profile. A standard or other specification to which a metadata record conforms.
description.en: Data structure for Application profile. A standard or other specification to which a metadata record conforms.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Media Type. A file format or physical medium.
description.en: Data structure for Media Type. A file format or physical medium.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro File. Downloadable file in given format.
description.en: Data structure for File. Downloadable file in given format.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Validation result. Class describing the result of validation testing. It may include validation of metadata, data and/or web services accessing the data.
description.en: Data structure for Validation result. Class describing the result of validation testing. It may include validation of metadata, data and/or web services accessing the data.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Subject scheme. Collection of subjects (keywords, concepts, classification codes) curated by a single source.
description.en: Data structure for Subject scheme. Collection of subjects (keywords, concepts, classification codes) curated by a single source.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Address. An "address representation" as conceptually defined by the INSPIRE Address Representation data type. The locn:addressId property may be used to link this locn:Address to other representations.
description.en: Data structure for Address. An "address representation" as conceptually defined by the INSPIRE Address Representation data type. The locn:addressId property may be used to link this locn:Address to other representations.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Provenance Statement. Any changes in ownership and custody of a resource since its creation that are significant for its authenticity, integrity, and interpretation.
description.en: Data structure for Provenance Statement. Any changes in ownership and custody of a resource since its creation that are significant for its authenticity, integrity, and interpretation.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Metadata to agent relationship. Relationship between metadata record and agent.
description.en: Data structure for Metadata to agent relationship. Relationship between metadata record and agent.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Metadata agent role type. An idea or notion; a unit of thought.
description.en: Data structure for Metadata agent role type. An idea or notion; a unit of thought.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Media Type. A file format or physical medium.
description.en: Data structure for Media Type. A file format or physical medium.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Subject. Subject, keyword, classification code, or key phrase describing the resource.
description.en: Data structure for Subject. Subject, keyword, classification code, or key phrase describing the resource.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Organization. Represents a collection of people organized together into a community or other social, commercial or political structure. The group has some common purpose or reason for existence which goes beyond the set of people belonging to it and can act as an Agent. Organizations are often decomposable into hierarchical structures.
description.en: Data structure for Organization. Represents a collection of people organized together into a community or other social, commercial or political structure. Organizations are often decomposable into hierarchical structures.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Subject scheme. Collection of subjects (keywords, concepts, classification codes) curated by a single source.
description.en: Data structure for Subject scheme. Collection of subjects (keywords, concepts, classification codes) curated by a single source.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Katalogizační záznam. Záznam v datovém katalogu popisující jednu datovou sadu či datovou službu.
description.en: Data structure for Metadata Record. Description of the metadata record of the dataset.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Katalog. Řízená kolekce metadat o datových sadách a datových službách
description.en: Data structure for Repository. A curated collection of metadata about resources.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Datová sada. Kolekce dat poskytovaná či řízená jedním zdrojem, která je k dispozici pro přístup či stažení v jednom či více formátech.
description.en: Data structure for Dataset. A collection of data, published or curated by a single source, and available for access or download in one or more representations.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Identifier. This is based on the UN/CEFACT Identifier class.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Alternate title. Alternate title f the resource
description.en: Data structure for Alternate title. Alternate title f the resource

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Geometry. The Geometry class provides the means to identify a location as a point, line, polygon, etc. expressed using coordinates in some coordinate reference system.
description.en: Data structure for Geometry. The Geometry class provides the means to identify a location as a point, line, polygon, etc. expressed using coordinates in some coordinate reference system.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Distribution - data service. Physical embodiment of the dataset as a particular data service.
description.en: Data structure for Distribution - data service. Physical embodiment of the dataset as a particular data service.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Documentation. A textual resource intended for human consumption that contains information about the data service.
description.en: Data structure for Documentation. A textual resource intended for human consumption that contains information about the data service.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Data service. Umístění či přístupový bod poskytující operace související s hledáním, přistupem k, či výkonem funkcí na datech či souvisejících zdrojích.
description.en: Data structure for Data service. A collection of operations that provides access to one or more datasets or data processing functions.

description.cs: Datová struktura pro Distribution - downloadable file. Physical embodiment of the dataset in a particular format.
